Revision history for PakMan by Rune Jacobsen

v0.2 Public beta version
   ·  Fixed the problem with Amiga Quake / QuakePlayer crashing with PAKs
      written by PakMan. Huge thanks to Sigbjørn Skjæret!

v0.1 Public beta version - debugging/enhancing

   ·  Won't allow renaming the <Parent> entry
   ·  "Rename" only registers a change if the string is actually changed
   ·  "Delete" only registers a change if any files are actually deleted
   ·  Added function to create a new PAK file
   ·  Added pattern gadget to load/create PAK file requester
   ·  No longer creates a directory that already exists
   ·  Allows creation of multiple directory levels in one go with MakeDir
   ·  Added the PAK optimization feature
   ·  Added important "About" logo
   ·  Localized the program
   ·  Added "Parent" button to GUI
   ·  Created a "cycle chain" for keyboard junkies
   ·  Won't allow creation of "noname" directories
   ·  Added a PAK information window
   ·  All windows now have the global menu strip
   ·  Fixed a few minor functionality issues
   ·  Made the PAK Info menuitem a CHECKIT item
   ·  Added a PUBSCREEN command line argument
   ·  Hopefully fixed the problem with bogus stuff in the MakeDir gadget

v0.0 Private beta version - building the basics

   ·  Added PAK directory reading
   ·  Added GUI
   ·  Added Extract function
   ·  Added Add function
   ·  Added menues
   ·  Added MakeDir function
   ·  Added rename function
   ·  Added lame about window

